.container
  .container-fluid.header
    .alert.alert-danger(role="alert", ng-show="$ctrl.wrongCredentials") Неверное имя пользователя или пароль!
  form.form-signin
    h3.form-signin-heading Вход
    label.sr-only(for="inputUsername") Email address
    input#inputUsername.form-control(type="text", placeholder="Username", required, autofocus, ng-model="$ctrl.username")
    label.sr-only(for="inputPassword") Password
    input#inputPassword.form-control(type="password", placeholder="Password", required, ng-model="$ctrl.password")
    button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block(type="submit", ng-click="$ctrl.login()") Войти